metadata.name: Act I - I've Attained A Purpose So Fulfilling
metadata.description:
20' X 20' 
Acrylic on Canvas with Matt Varnish  

After years of searching... I am finally realizing the potential of my own power. My power is to tell stories through these paintings and now... no one can stop me. I am finally Free.  

Original Painting is Redeemable.
